# Inspecting Dataset

```{r}
# Load Dataset
df_100 <- fetch_subset(df_file_path, col_names = c(-1), nrows = c(1, 100), chunk_size = 1e5)

```

## List of Column names 

```{r}
col_names <- names(df_100)
print(col_names)
```
## \# of Observations

```{r}
nrows <- nrow(fread(df_file_path, select = 1, header = TRUE))
print(nrows)

```
